title: Faster Ansible playbook iteration with tags and Vagrant snapshots
url: https://gist.github.com/5f3be54ac59d7f0652bd9b803b79f70c
summary: Last couple of months, I had to write a large amount of Ansible playbooks, to the point that the slow write/test cycle became a major annoyance. What seemed to work well for me was a mix between Ansible tags and Vagrant snapshots.
